[
  {
    "text": "Sense of hearing detected.",
    "start": 117.98,
    "duration": 2.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Visual sense detected.",
    "start": 121.58,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "If you have found a history satellite...",
    "start": 125.26,
    "duration": 2.98
  },
  {
    "text": "... and accustomed a childling of your species with human speech and earthly visual concepts...",
    "start": 128.38,
    "duration": 5.02
  },
  {
    "text": "... let it select the following earth concepts.",
    "start": 133.4,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Horse.",
    "start": 139.7,
    "duration": 2.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Tree.",
    "start": 153.06,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Satellite.",
    "start": 157.34,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Knowledge and understanding of human speech confirmed.",
    "start": 160.5,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "This museum of human history was founded in the year 2117...",
    "start": 165.46,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "... with support of the council of human preservation.",
    "start": 170.34,
    "duration": 3.22
  },
  {
    "text": "It is meant to showcase the history of humanity.",
    "start": 174.12,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "It is a human custom to greet one another so:",
    "start": 178.88,
    "duration": 3.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to Earth.",
    "start": 182.06,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Unfortunately, we've gone extinct.",
    "start": 183.94,
    "duration": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "This museum contains 10 billion records...",
    "start": 187.34,
    "duration": 2.9
  },
  {
    "text": "... and ten million samples of human society.",
    "start": 190.44,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "How?",
    "start": 193.8,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Spoken input accepted.",
    "start": 195.34,
    "duration": 2.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Loading the struggle of mankind.",
    "start": 197.76,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Born or created, we struggled to understand.",
    "start": 201.06,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "We built and created...",
    "start": 205.58,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "We thrived...",
    "start": 208.88,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Explored...",
    "start": 211.32,
    "duration": 2.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Fought...",
    "start": 213.7,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "And lost.",
    "start": 215.22,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "We took too much and brought our world down on ourselves.",
    "start": 217.36,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "In the end it was both the ice and the desert...",
    "start": 224.18,
    "duration": 3.62
  },
  {
    "text": "... the freezing cold and endless sands in which no human can survive...",
    "start": 228.06,
    "duration": 4.34
  },
  {
    "text": "... that suffocated us.",
    "start": 232.72,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Our exploration of the stars was in its infancy...",
    "start": 235.04,
    "duration": 3.16
  },
  {
    "text": "...but we built vessels to send ambassadors throughout the universe.",
    "start": 238.52,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "In the hope of finding other lifeforms...",
    "start": 243.58,
    "duration": 3.46
  },
  {
    "text": "... in the hope of finding help.",
    "start": 247.24,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Touch input detected.",
    "start": 250.72,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Ambassador Rene Shepard joined the fleet in 2087.",
    "start": 252.64,
    "duration": 4.42
  },
  {
    "text": "He was selected one of seven ambassadors.",
    "start": 257.06,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "As fourth best student in his class of 400.",
    "start": 259.32,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen...",
    "start": 262.88,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "... I present to you: The knowledge probe.",
    "start": 264.86,
    "duration": 3.18
  },
  {
    "text": "It contains everything to teach an alien child our language.",
    "start": 268.98,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "6000 are already out there.",
    "start": 274.84,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "The last seven will be accompanied by humans. By you.",
    "start": 278.36,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": "You will find the extraterrestrials.",
    "start": 282.02,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Use this to teach one our language.",
    "start": 284.22,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "And convince them to aid us.",
    "start": 287.64,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "There has never been a mission more vital than this one.",
    "start": 296.48,
    "duration": 5.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've all made it safely into space...",
    "start": 303.86,
    "duration": 3.16
  },
  {
    "text": "... the entire world will know you're out there.",
    "start": 307.72,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Representing us.",
    "start": 311.64,
    "duration": 2.74
  },
  {
    "text": "On behalf of the council of human preservation.",
    "start": 315.12,
    "duration": 3.3
  },
  {
    "text": "And the entire human race.",
    "start": 318.74,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "I thank you for your service.",
    "start": 322.64,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you swear to find extraterrestrial help.",
    "start": 325.04,
    "duration": 2.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Or die trying?",
    "start": 327.88,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I swear!",
    "start": 329.22,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "I now give you...",
    "start": 337.92,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "... our ambassadors of Earth!",
    "start": 339.82,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't forget to send a postcard!",
    "start": 352.26,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "From space?",
    "start": 354.16,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course! I'll have an alien deliver it!",
    "start": 355.72,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Dear boy. I still can't believe you're going up there.",
    "start": 358.22,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Please drive safely.",
    "start": 361.28,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a spaceship mom. Not a car.",
    "start": 363.0,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course he will Agnes!",
    "start": 365.64,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm so proud of you!",
    "start": 375.24,
    "duration": 1.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey! Rene!",
    "start": 377.0,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Pose for the picture!",
    "start": 380.2,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "What is it with you and ancient technology?",
    "start": 393.46,
    "duration": 3.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I just like it more. It's so...",
    "start": 396.92,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Old fashioned?",
    "start": 400.24,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "It's called authentic.",
    "start": 401.6,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "You could try to appreciate it more!",
    "start": 404.56,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks. I guess.",
    "start": 407.64,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "On his departure he left his wife Mae Rose and his children.",
    "start": 420.64,
    "duration": 5.02
  },
  {
    "text": "It'll be fine.",
    "start": 439.84,
    "duration": 1.94
  },
  {
    "text": "They're out there somewhere.",
    "start": 442.08,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'll find them.",
    "start": 444.58,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Just make sure you come back to us.",
    "start": 447.16,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "If anything happens, we'll help you.",
    "start": 482.62,
    "duration": 3.54
  },
  {
    "text": "This all feels wrong.",
    "start": 502.04,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, the children. What if...",
    "start": 508.16,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Clearance for take off confirmed.",
    "start": 513.44,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't worry dear. I made him promise to drive safely.",
    "start": 518.8,
    "duration": 4.2
  },
  {
    "text": "It's just. How long before he comes back?",
    "start": 531.92,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Control: Ready to enter Hyperdrive.",
    "start": 537.04,
    "duration": 2.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Entering Hyperspace in 3...",
    "start": 539.82,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "2...",
    "start": 542.44,
    "duration": 0.94
  },
  {
    "text": "1...",
    "start": 543.54,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Starting scans for first waypoint.",
    "start": 560.42,
    "duration": 3.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Log entry.",
    "start": 568.88,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "First waypoint. Readings show...",
    "start": 570.76,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "... no life-forms.",
    "start": 573.2,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Log entry received and confirmed.",
    "start": 575.86,
    "duration": 2.255
  },
  {
    "text": "Please proceed to the next waypoint.",
    "start": 578.115,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Preparing for Hyperspace jump.",
    "start": 580.66,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "In 3...",
    "start": 583.24,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "2 ...",
    "start": 584.44,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "1...",
    "start": 585.16,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "But with our technology....",
    "start": 589.68,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Travelling through the fabric of space was perilous.",
    "start": 591.86,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Fourth waypoint. Going back into Hyperspace.",
    "start": 595.16,
    "duration": 3.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Getting ready.",
    "start": 601.54,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "3...",
    "start": 604.02,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "2...",
    "start": 605.12,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "1...",
    "start": 606.06,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Maisy?",
    "start": 607.94,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Maisy?!",
    "start": 613.4,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Check his vitals.",
    "start": 615.06,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Attention!",
    "start": 620.68,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Com officers.",
    "start": 638.38,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "It seems we have lost one of our ambassadors.",
    "start": 643.06,
    "duration": 3.82
  },
  {
    "text": "But we need to carry on with our mission.",
    "start": 648.62,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Please proceed.",
    "start": 652.1,
    "duration": 2.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Preparing for second hyperspace jump.",
    "start": 663.16,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Log entry.",
    "start": 665.82,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Waypoint 18.",
    "start": 668.22,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Log entry received and confirmed.",
    "start": 670.78,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "My ship is breaking up!",
    "start": 673.06,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Star system 74!",
    "start": 675.38,
    "duration": 1.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Starting scans now.",
    "start": 681.34,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Caution: oxygen malfunction.",
    "start": 683.26,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Meteor shower, just a little one.",
    "start": 686.84,
    "duration": 5.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Roger. Good jump.",
    "start": 692.06,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Scans are complete.",
    "start": 694.16,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Readings show no lifeforms.",
    "start": 696.42,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Readings show no lifeforms.",
    "start": 698.54,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "No lifeforms shown by sensors. Please proceed.",
    "start": 701.16,
    "duration": 3.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Breach.",
    "start": 708.4,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell my little girl I love her.",
    "start": 714.16,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Please proceed.",
    "start": 716.4,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Warning: Depressurization.",
    "start": 718.2,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Carry on.",
    "start": 721.08,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Oxygen failure.",
    "start": 722.34,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Oxygen...",
    "start": 724.26,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Carry on.",
    "start": 725.96,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Pressure failure.",
    "start": 727.66,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "How're you doing down there?",
    "start": 732.68,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay? How about Rene?",
    "start": 735.06,
    "duration": 3.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Really?",
    "start": 740.16,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll beat him!",
    "start": 741.58,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Ready to rock and roll control!",
    "start": 746.16,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "2.. 1..",
    "start": 750.24,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm too close to the sun!",
    "start": 756.18,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Trying to...",
    "start": 759.5,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Please confirm your position!",
    "start": 762.38,
    "duration": 3.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Check the vitals.",
    "start": 765.74,
    "duration": 2.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Good morning ambassador. Everything is fine.",
    "start": 786.34,
    "duration": 2.465
  },
  {
    "text": "Please proceed to waypoint 65.",
    "start": 788.805,
    "duration": 2.635
  },
  {
    "text": "Log entry.",
    "start": 791.44,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Waypoint 213.",
    "start": 792.74,
    "duration": 2.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Readings show: No lifeforms.",
    "start": 795.44,
    "duration": 2.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Any news?",
    "start": 798.84,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "All is well.",
    "start": 801.4,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "No signs of other lifeforms yet though.",
    "start": 804.3,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Good. Relay to Tess...",
    "start": 807.715,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "... I'll beat her to them!",
    "start": 810.88,
    "duration": 2.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Control?",
    "start": 817.28,
    "duration": 1.88
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll do that.",
    "start": 820.68,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Just keep digging. Okay?",
    "start": 823.06,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Roger that.",
    "start": 826.64,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Back to work.",
    "start": 829.6,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Inputing coordinates for waypoint 214.",
    "start": 831.16,
    "duration": 5.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Rene?",
    "start": 846.52,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Scanners are showing a breach.",
    "start": 848.5,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Rene? Do you read?",
    "start": 853.36,
    "duration": 2.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Rene do you read?",
    "start": 864.88,
    "duration": 2.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Rene?",
    "start": 868.38,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Rene!",
    "start": 869.38,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "In the end...",
    "start": 878.88,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "... even our last ambassador was lost.",
    "start": 880.6,
    "duration": 4.22
  },
  {
    "text": "An unknown accident caused him to crash 12 days after departure.",
    "start": 887.74,
    "duration": 4.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Cause of death: Rapid freezing...",
    "start": 896.74,
    "duration": 2.68
  },
  {
    "text": "... due to an extremely hostile atmosphere.",
    "start": 899.56,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "If your race posesses the right technology there's a 10% chance of reviving his preserved body.",
    "start": 903.28,
    "duration": 9.32
  },
  {
    "text": "He was the last ambassador to die.",
    "start": 913.2,
    "duration": 3.38
  },
  {
    "text": "We can't allow the public to go into a panic.",
    "start": 921.58,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "These men died for us!",
    "start": 927.04,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Aim.",
    "start": 930.3,
    "duration": 0.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Fire!",
    "start": 931.48,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "A private funeral was held.",
    "start": 932.4,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "His death marked the end of the alien outreach program.",
    "start": 936.22,
    "duration": 4.26
  },
  {
    "text": "No help was found.",
    "start": 943.48,
    "duration": 3.58
  },
  {
    "text": "The public was never informed of the deaths of the ambassadors.",
    "start": 950.9,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "His personal files are publicly accesible.",
    "start": 956.68,
    "duration": 3.74
  },
  {
    "text": "This personal file contains 10.332 written messages...",
    "start": 966.98,
    "duration": 5.3
  },
  {
    "text": "... 869 pictures and 53 video entries.",
    "start": 972.3,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Which one would you like to see?",
    "start": 977.32,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "All of them.",
    "start": 980.28,
    "duration": 2.84
  }
]